verbose_text: Our observations strongly suggest that, in addition to Centrin3 required to build the ALF that guides the new basal body during its assembly, ICL1e is necessary to recruit Centrin3 in the proximity of the striated fibre where the pro basal body is assembled during duplication.
evidence: Centrin3 required to build the ALF that guides the new basal body during its assembly              , ICL1e is necessary
